txt.en: 'While you were busy about the Rosigil, I had one of my men deliver a new box of pins. Take it up, will you, and replace the ones that you found filed down. There is also some rope which you can use to replace the frayed bundles you found.'

An investigation revealed that many of the post pins and bundles of rope on the Rosigil and docks were intentionally damaged. They must be replaced, for if left in their current state they could endanger the crew.
You should let Annúngil know that you have replaced the damaged pins and piles of rope on the Rosigil.\n\nThe wharf master is on a dock in the Dol Amroth bay.

Wharf master Annúngil has asked you to replace the damaged ropes and pins on the Rosigil. You should pick up the box of pins and bundles of new rope.\n\nThe box of pins and the rope are next to Annúngil, on the docks in the Dol Amroth bay.
Pick up the bundle of rope
TBD - 'Is it done? Excellent. I know not who is behind this, but I am determined to find out!'
Pick up the box of pins
You are now armed with fresh pins and tightly woven ropes. You should replace the pins on the Rosigil and the rope on the docks.\n\nThe Rosigil is moored in the Dol Amroth bay.
'Is it done? Excellent. I know not who is behind this, but I am determined to find out!'
